title: Marumagan
subTitle: Thangarasu, a humble tailor, falls for Manjula, the daughter of a corrupt politician. Subsequently, her mother opposes their love while her father seeks to exploit their relationship for his own gain.

title: January 1st
subTitle: When a series of mysterious murders rock the city, a courageous inspector, Mano, sets out to capture the culprit and restore order.

title: Aradhanai
subTitle: Indu and Vasanth are college mates who are madly in love until they split due to a misunderstanding. Unable to bear the separation, Vasanth resorts to black magic to woo Indu back.

title: Idhu Namma Aalu
subTitle: Gopalsamy, a poor graduate from a lower caste, assumes the identity of a higher caste to escape his financial struggles. However, complications arise when Banu, the daughter of a priest, marries him, unaware of his true social background.

title: Moodu Mandhiram
subTitle: Dilip, a wealthy and boastful man, gets into trouble after he gets into an altercation with Kalpana, the district collector. Later, he plans on making her fall in love with him to seek revenge.

title: Pullakuttikaran
subTitle: Ammu, a young girl, falls in love with Veeraiyan, a pickpocket and marries him. Later, their past troubles with an evil politician catch up to them.

title: Kaivantha Kalai
subTitle: Kannan and his father scam their fellow villagers until Kannan falls in love with a girl, Kausalya. Her only demand is for him to leave his crooked ways if he wants a future with her.

title: Chinna Marumagal
subTitle: The eldest daughter-in-law of a family faces various hardships at the hands of her mother-in-law. The youngest daughter-in-law teaches her a lesson and makes her realise her mistakes.
